11 (e) Vermont residents receiving health care services at a hospital shall not
12 be balance billed or otherwise charged for receiving the services except to the
13 extent of any applicable cost-sharing amounts established by the Agency by
14 rule.
15 § 1844. GLOBAL HOSPITAL BUDGETS
16 (a)(1) Annually, the Green Mountain Care Board, in collaboration with the
17 Secretary of Human Services, shall develop a global hospital budget for the
18 State and individual hospital budgets for each hospital located in Vermont. In
19 developing the global hospital budget, the Board shall consider the Health
20 Resource Allocation Plan developed pursuant to 18 V.S.A. § 9405, the hospital
21 budget review process set forth in 18 V.S.A. § 9456, the negotiated global
